!!VRz10:S^Welcome, travelers.  What brings a warrior and a cadre-mage to
my humble house, on the shimmering shores of Silver Rune?
My name?  Well, some call me ... Tim.^;
!!VRz12:S^Tim the Enchanter^;
!!VRz13:S^..\Data\SND_Tim1.jpg^;
!!IF:D33/z10/0/z12/z13 ;
!!IF:F33/0/0/0/0/0;
!!IF:E99/33;
!!VRz10:S^You want my help, so you can restore power to the Portals, and
seek your doom against Megathon?  You seem little more than children!
You should leave here and quickly!  There is a killer rabbit nearby,
a foul, cruel rodent with nasty teeth and a viscious streak.^;
!!VRz12:S^Tim the Enchanter^;
!!VRz13:S^..\Data\SND_Tim1.jpg^;
!!IF:D33/z10/0/z12/z13 ;
!!IF:F33/0/0/0/0/0;
